    public class Query4_Auctions_Items_CoProcessFunction
extends org.apache.flink.streaming.api.functions.co.CoProcessFunction<org.dima.dominikschroeck.largestate.Events.NexMark.AuctionEvent,org.dima.dominikschroeck.largestate.Events.NexMark.NewItemEvent,org.dima.dominikschroeck.largestate.Events.NexMark.AuctionEvent_Category>
    CoProcess function for Query 4. Connects AuctionEvents and ItemEvents. It collects one Item from the item stream and many auctions. Streams keyed by Item_id. Enriches the AuctionEvent Stream with the Category_id which is only visible in the ItemEvents.
